valgrind
    valgrind --leak-check=full ./dwmstatus

signalhandling
    - SIGUSR1: refresh all caches

informations (information namespace):
    - time (%H:%M:%S)
    - CPU utilization (reserve 2 digits)
    - MEM used (reserve 4 digits)
    - battery (only if present, reserve 2 digits)

    example:
    0.37 0.18 0.09 [Des kleinen Herzens le..] 0+2 54%  534M 42Â°  4% 14:55:32
